For Open Source Conference 2015 Oita NetBSD booth
 demonstration use, I've updated allwinner image.

 https://www.facebook.com/events/383442128496493/
 https://www.facebook.com/NetBSD.jp 
 https://www.soum.co.jp/~jun/OSC2015oita.pdf

- NetBSD 7.99.4 earmv7hf beagleboard.img.gz base
- Connect HDMI,USB Keyboard,USB Mouse,Ether(dhcpd and ntpd will work)
- login root (no passwd)
- startx ,and icewm running.
- mikutter and so on.

Features:
  - fit size for 2GB SD Card
  - with X11
  - Recent current Cubieboard2 kernel
  - pkgsrc: 2015-01-31 tree inside.
  - pre-build packages
    ftp://ftp.netbsd.org/pub/NetBSD/misc/jun/allwinner/earmv7hf/2015-02-07/

